Begin telaseroDisable

short telenable
short nolore

if ( telenable == -1 )
	return
endif

if ( GetJournalIndex FG_Telasero < 10 )
	if ( GetDisabled == 0 )
		Disable
	endif
	Return
endif

if ( GetJournalIndex FG_Telasero >= 10 )
	if ( GetDisabled == 1 )
		Enable
		set telenable to -1
	endif
endif

End telaseroDisable
